text: The 2020 United States presidential election in Vermont was held on Tuesday, November 3, 2020, as part of the 2020 United States presidential election. Former Vice President Joe Biden, and his running mate U.S. SenatorKamala Harris had won 3 electoral votes in the Electoral College. == References == Category:2020 United States presidential election Category:2020 in Vermont
title: 2020 United States presidential election in Vermont
